            <title>[LU-16512] Check index when handling netdev events</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16512</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In some situations, it can exist an interface with the same name as an existing one.&lt;/p&gt;

